{"id": "1215241196784459796", "channel_id": "1214492945311600640", "type": 0, "author_id": "286449214110564353", "author_name": "_glass0fuwu_", "author_bot": false, "content": "uid：100373509\n雖然說是剛入坑的萌新，但應該也能分享一下？\n被朋友誘惑說有小男孩（圖魯）就來了，沒想到還要等復刻(´•ω•`)\n後面朋友又說現在up的粉毛可以搭，所以就想努力肝一肝\n目前是登入第六天、19級，共計93抽連歪三次，沒想到開局就喜提大保底😭\n\n題外話，我本身蠻排斥卡牌相關的遊戲，因為自己玩超爛，加上也不怎麼想動腦\n結果現在很努力的在越級打主線肝銀芯，突出的就是一個本斥但真香\n（希望圖魯復刻時別抽歪了我心臟承受不起TT", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:14:39.403000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1215241196582993940", "filename": "Screenshot_20240307_175827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 132462, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1214492945311600640/1215241196582993940/Screenshot_20240307_175827.jpg?ex=69ccf00f&is=69cb9e8f&hm=3f806248312cf15e814b2b76aa6e7206ce853216bf7c6e5af739e18fedd53002&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1214492945311600640", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "百日慶典", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
{"id": "1215243886666973235", "channel_id": "1214492945311600640", "type": 0, "author_id": "333957728466894851", "author_name": "lanl4n", "author_bot": false, "content": "uid:100199684\n最難忘的根本是抽卡體驗,只有保底才會出金是什麼樣的體驗😇 \n起初只是被美術風格與主打克系內容吸引,但後來越玩越有趣\n劇情文本呈現很好,幾乎可以彌補畫面不足這件事\n策略玩法也很有難度(打到腦溢血),初期深海玩起來跟下水道一樣,但隨著日後更新與墨菲的實裝也讓深海玩家玩起來沒那麼坐牢\n非常感謝官方帶給我們這款遊戲🍟", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:25:20.721000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:26:26.670000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1215243886373380096", "filename": "Screenshot_2024.03.07_18.13.41.473.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1144363, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1214492945311600640/1215243886373380096/Screenshot_2024.03.07_18.13.41.473.png?ex=69ccf290&is=69cba110&hm=b06f02bd57451f1414d5fa48022acf881c4675c0b2093eb2ae5b843a7f5b6e94&"}, {"id": "1215243886797262868", "filename": "Screenshot_2024.03.07_18.15.59.606.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1573149, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1214492945311600640/1215243886797262868/Screenshot_2024.03.07_18.15.59.606.png?ex=69ccf290&is=69cba110&hm=6d9e0a5ec8a13da6a8388040e18a5ddaa8856f5bc7c712f846a2b628f8def678&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1214492945311600640", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "百日慶典", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135978832859146"]}
